snippet: Senator Elizabeth Warren, who has been mentioned as a possible presidential candidate in 2016, confirmed she would not run.
abstract: Massachusetts Sen Elizabeth Warren pledges to finish her entire term, saying she will not run for president in 2016 as some had hoped.
lead_paragraph: Senator Elizabeth Warren, who has been mentioned as a possible presidential candidate in 2016, confirmed she would not run.

headline.main: Massachusetts: Warren Rules Out a Run for President
headline.print_headline: Massachusetts: Warren Rules Out a Run For President
